NOONSOB
v.
STATE of NC 131P16-6 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Somchoi Noonsab, for Noonsab, Somchoi. Somchoi Noorsob, for Noorsob, Somchoi.

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of March 2018."
